---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const focus = [
  { label: '01 · win',  title: 'Active Directory',     desc: 'Kerberos abuse, BloodHound paths, NTLM relay, certificate services, full domain compromise.' },
  { label: '02 · web',  title: 'Web Exploitation',     desc: 'SQLi, SSRF, auth bypass, chained logic flaws via Burp Suite as a scalpel.' },
  { label: '03 · priv', title: 'Privilege Escalation', desc: 'Linux + Windows — weak services, SUID chains, DLL hijack, token impersonation.' },
  { label: '04 · hash', title: 'Password Attacks',     desc: 'Hashcat rules, Responder, Pass-the-Hash, credential hunting on AD.' },
  { label: '05 · code', title: 'Python Automation',    desc: 'Recon orchestration — nmap + ffuf + gobuster into a single pipeline.' },
  { label: '06 · net',  title: 'Networking',           desc: 'CCNA in progress — routing, VLANs, ACLs, the plumbing under every box.' },
];
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="Mike — offensive security student at Hogeschool Utrecht, HackTheBox Master.">
  <section class="page-head">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="page-kicker" data-reveal>/ about</div>
      <h1 class="page-title" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">A student who <span class="italic">breaks things</span><br/>for a grade.</h1>
      <p class="page-sub" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">Offensive security student at Hogeschool Utrecht. 24 years old. Most at home inside an Active Directory that wishes I wasn't.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <aside class="about-side" data-reveal>
          <div class="about-fact">
            <div class="about-label">Identity</div>
            <div class="about-key">Certifa</div>
            <div class="about-val">Mike · 24 y/o</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-fact">
            <div class="about-label">Location</div>
            <div class="about-key">Utrecht</div>
            <div class="about-val">Netherlands</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-fact">
            <div class="about-label">Studying at</div>
            <div class="about-key">Hogeschool Utrecht</div>
            <div class="about-val">Cybersecurity &amp; Cloud · BSc</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-fact">
            <div class="about-label">Primary Platform</div>
            <div class="about-key">HackTheBox</div>
            <div class="about-val">Master · peak Pro Hacker</div>
          </div>
          <div class="about-fact">
            <div class="about-label">Attack OS</div>
            <div class="about-key">Parrot</div>
            <div class="about-val">tmux · vim · burp</div>
          </div>
        </aside>

        <div class="about-body" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
          <p>My primary playground is <b>HackTheBox</b> — <code>50+</code> machines across Easy → Insane. I write everything up <em>after the box retires</em>, because the lesson lives in the explanation, not the root flag.</p>

          <p>On the <b>Windows</b> side: Kerberos abuse — AS-REP, Kerberoast, delegation chains — BloodHound path-finding, NTLM relay, and certificate services abuse. I run a <b>Server 2022 DC</b> and two workstations at home, so nothing I do on HTB feels unfamiliar when I sit down at it.</p>

          <p>On <b>Linux</b>: privesc through weak services, SUID chains, misconfigured cron. On the <b>web</b>: SQLi, SSRF, auth bypass, chained logic bugs. Burp as a scalpel — not a shotgun.</p>

          <p>I glue my recon together with <b>Python</b>: <code>nmap</code>, <code>ffuf</code>, <code>gobuster</code> piped into a single report template. Currently grinding <b>CCNA</b> because the best attackers actually understand the network they're living in. Next on the cert list: <b>CJCA</b> and <b>CPTS</b>.</p>

          <div class="focus-grid">
            {focus.map((f) => (
              <div class="focus-card">
                <div class="fc-label">{f.label}</div>
                <div class="fc-title">{f.title}</div>
                <div class="fc-desc">{f.desc}</div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .wrap { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 32px; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .wrap { padding: 0 20px; } }

  .about-grid {
    padding: 96px 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 260px 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; padding: 56px 0; }
  }

  .about-side { position: sticky; top: 100px; align-self: start; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    /* Compact 2-column fact grid so the bio starts sooner */
    .about-side {
      position: static;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px 20px;
    }
  }

  .about-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--fg-3);
    letter-spacing: 0.14em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .about-key { font-size: 16px; color: var(--fg); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .about-val { font-size: 14px; color: var(--fg-2); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-label { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .about-val { margin-bottom: 0; }
  }

  .about-body p {
    font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--fg-2);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 700px;
  }
  .about-body p b { color: var(--fg); font-weight: 500; }
  .about-body p em {
    font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif;
    font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 400;
  }
  .about-body p code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: var(--bg-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .focus-grid {
    margin-top: 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 700px) { .focus-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .focus-card {
    background: var(--bg-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 22px;
    transition: border-color .2s ease, background .2s ease;
  }
  @media (hover: hover) {
    .focus-card:hover { border-color: var(--line-2); background: var(--bg-3); }
  }
  .focus-card .fc-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px; color: var(--fg-3);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .focus-card .fc-title {
    font-size: 17px; font-weight: 500; color: var(--fg);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .focus-card .fc-desc {
    color: var(--fg-2);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
